VEGANS PAY ATTENTION TO YOUR PROTEIN SOURCES‚Ä¶‚Å£
‚Å£
If your goal is body re composition, you need sufficient protein intake (2-3g per kg of lean body mass) and some sort of progressive resistance training to stop the catabolism of muscle mass.‚Å£
‚Å£
Now, all proteins are made of building blocks called amino acids, BUT not all proteins contain all the amino acids you require.‚Å£
‚Å£
There are some amino acids that the human body can't manufacture and these amino acids are called the essential amino acids because you have to consume them through your diet.‚Å£
‚Å£
These include:‚Å£
‚Å£
Histidine‚Å£
Isoleucine‚Å£
Leucine‚Å£
Lysine‚Å£
Methionine‚Å£
Phenylalanine‚Å£
Threonine‚Å£
Tryptophan‚Å£
Valine‚Å£
‚Å£
Animal proteins (eggs, whey, red meat, fish, poultry) all contain every single one of these essential amino acids, so they're called complete proteins.‚Å£
‚Å£
Plant proteins are a little different.‚Å£
‚Å£
Each plant that you eat has a different amino acid profile. For example, grains and cereals are extremely low in lysine. ‚Å£
‚Å£
Grains and legumes are called complementary proteins because when you combine them, you get all of the essential amino acids. ‚Å£
‚Å£
So here are some complete protein combinations to play around with;‚Å£
‚Å£
üç£ Lentils + rice‚Å£
üçû Hummus + pita bread‚Å£
üçöPeas + Rice‚Å£
ü•ú Tofu + sesame‚Å£
üåÆ Beans + Almonds‚Å£
üå∞ Whole wheat toast + nut butter‚Å£
‚Å£
** Remember with these duos comes added calories from carbohydrates and fats‚Å£
‚Å£

The best muffins ever!!!!
Banana Blueberry Muffin üçå ü´ê
Gluten free and packed with protein ‚ô•Ô∏è

@fengshuiflow  @rosycheeksss 

2 cups Organic Quinoa Flour
1 1/2 tsp Baking Soda
1 tsp Ground Cinnamon
1/4 tsp Sea Salt
3 Tbsp Unsalted Butter
2 Eggs
1 cup Milk
1/2 cup Maple Syrup
1 Banana smashed
1 cup Blueberries

Pre-heat oven to 375¬∞F. Line a muffin tin with paper liners or grease well with butter or oil.
Mix dry ingredients in a bowl and set aside. Melt butter in a saucepan on low heat.
In a large bowl add eggs and beat together. Add milk, melted butter, maple syrup and smashed banana to eggs and mix well. Add dry ingredients to wet ingredients and gently fold in blueberries.
Bake for 25 minutes until the tops spring back when lightly touched.

LEARN HOW TO TIME YOUR MEALS üëá

Timing is everything. Our body's have an internal clock which follows roughly the 24 hour day cycle (aka circadian rhythm).

There are periods of the day in which light exposure and temperature are higher, cortisol, alertness, coordination, etc. 

Knowing how to manipulate these each day and learning how to schedule your eating window around this will keep you lean, healthy and working optimally! 

If you want to learn how this is done and can be applied to you, please comment below or shoot me a DM.

When creating this blog, I came up with the name Expedition Eats as a motivation to explore nola‚Äôs rich culture through the lens of its diverse eateries. And this expedition of flavors from @addisnola was exactly the type of experience I set out to find!
‚Ä¢
‚Ä¢
@addisnola serves authentic Ethiopian cuisine in a shared experience that fosters a sense of community and love! Addis offers an array of dishes sure to tame the wildest appetite, from vegetarian to lamb and everything in between. It might be easier to tell you what we didn‚Äôt order, but pictured on our shared plate are chicken and shrimp tibs, doro wot, red lentils, collard greens, cabbage, and beets! The doro wot and red lentils were my absolute fave - thanks @eatenpathnola for the recommendations! And every meal is served with injera, a spongy flatbread that acts as your edible utensil.
‚Ä¢
‚Ä¢
Thank you Prince for making my first visit an unforgettable experience! This month and every month, it‚Äôs so important that we continue to support Black-owned businesses and celebrate Black History.
